Name or body： which is closer? Body or possessions： which means more? Gain
 or loss： Which one hurts?
Extreme love exacts a great price. Many possessions entail a heavy loss.
Know what is enough - Abuse nothing. Know when to stop - Harm nothing. This
 is how to last for a long time.
